Type: Package
Package: NUIMM
Title: NUIMM: Network-based Utility for Integrating Microbiome and
    Metabolome data
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Bowornpol Nu-im [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Bowornpol Nu-im <bowornpol.nui@mahidol.ac.th>
Description: A comprehensive R package designed for integrating microbiome
    and metabolome data through multi-layered network analysis. It enables
    network construction and advanced analyses, including hub
    identification, pathfinding, and node prioritization, to uncover
    context-specific biological associations.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/bowornpol/NUIMM
